Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙也好 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風馬的忍者們也好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.25,0:01:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了一族著想的心情和我們完全一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用了想讓一族復興的風馬眾人的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要把你打個落花流水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.15,0:02:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,恐怖 大蛇丸的老巢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次輕易就中綱手婆婆麻藥的好色仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.55,0:02:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次居然看穿莎莎美會暗中下藥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自來也大人的洞察力如此敏銳 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.15,0:02:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美提到半崎時說他是個叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.32,0:02:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點引起了我的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個半崎已經把所有事都告訴我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸來到這個國家的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我族想借助他的力量復興
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有人感受到了他的邪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不願與他聯手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你們被逐出了村子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:02:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:03:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被逐肯定是大蛇丸的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從此便背負著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻礙一族復興的叛徒這個罪名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美既然說半崎是個叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明她多少和大蛇丸有些瓜葛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.15,0:03:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 好色仙人 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是為了見到嵐哥哥才…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我只能做這些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自來也大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美因為一心想見自己的表哥才…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你原諒她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也求求您了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者的規矩是很嚴格的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無罪赦免肯定不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就先懲罰我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答應過莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會幫她找到表哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果食言的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就違背了我的忍道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自來也大人 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我又沒要把她怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半崎一直擔心你離開了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑去了大蛇丸那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先帶我們去大蛇丸的老巢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後立刻去半崎所在的旅店街
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏等我們回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.95,0:05:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是最適合你的懲罰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自來也大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色仙人 我對你刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 自來也大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為半崎的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在風馬酒館裏享受了各種特殊服務
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以莎莎美的事當然要關照一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你還是這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是看錯你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾一次沒什麼關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成年人是需要交際的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就交給我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回旅店街的時候小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會把你的嵐哥哥給帶回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵐哥哥就拜託大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.75,0:06:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美 你就放一百個心等著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太得意忘形了 笨蛋鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助…就在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來入口好像只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是中了埋伏的話 就無路可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 現在也只能硬著頭皮上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太心急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然闖進三只大老鼠 太過顯眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先讓一個不顯眼的傢伙去試試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通靈之術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.95,0:07:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛤蟆…會說話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 這傢伙叫蛤蟆吉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛤蟆吉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想拜託你去打探一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小事一樁 包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說 總讓人感覺不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒發現什麼奇怪的動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來入口並沒有設伏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵐哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊看來也比較安全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.15,0:08:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們只能兵分三路了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據我的直覺 應該是中間這條
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候必須得慎重行動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我認為是這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種做法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我的有什麼區別啊 好色仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣氛問題嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半小時之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果還是什麼都沒發現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.15,0:08:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就回到這裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到沒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.25,0:09:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個一起行動為好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是通往地獄的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道會跑出魔鬼還是大蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要有心理準備哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 我們就走中間這條了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.15,0:09:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就走這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脂粉的香氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.95,0:09:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在引誘我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就自動送上門了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朋自遠方來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奉大蛇丸大人之命迎接您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是狐狸精之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道我是不是狐狸精
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就過來看看我有沒有尾巴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這條路我走對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那裏怎麼樣了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道這裏會有什麼樣的陷阱埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己剛剛才說要小心一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是很巧妙的機關啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被卡在裏面了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫那麼淒慘 我以為…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快救救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我了 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你趕快離開這個陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定趕上來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好了 一定要來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒裏沒動手腳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟要玩什麼花招呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是音隱村
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算用樂技嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音律不單是為了客人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是為我而彈奏的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音律會奏出女人何樣的心聲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了弔唁我自己的樂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用女色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太小看我自來也了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把客人送到那個世界去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我最後的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活動屋頂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須得趕快離開這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠困難的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借個手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中查克拉 使出螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的倒輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身體已經伸展到極限了 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽筋了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 必須趕快想點辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我鬆開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 這不是鳴人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛤蟆吉 找到出路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛 不知道 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被水給沖到這裏來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能不要緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人可真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是回去比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想不到你竟然能到這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音是兜…前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是諷刺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在木葉舉行的中忍選拔考試中墊底的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然到了這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並非一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人和自來也大人稍後也會趕到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空關心佐助的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如替鳴人和自來也大人擔擔心比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們倆說不定已經離開這個世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自來也大人和鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會這麼輕易就被幹掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次你又拖鳴人的後腿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心的話 你就親自去確認一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說 你害怕我的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢從柱子後邊出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有像你這樣拖後腿的同伴在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多條命也不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.40,0:18:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是替身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有認真戰鬥的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 你就這麼點實力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該做個了結了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再讓大蛇丸大人這麼白白等下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 該開始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卷軸的爭奪之戰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會傾盡全力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經脫胎換骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.90,0:20:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼虛張聲勢也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.80,0:22:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種壓迫感是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙腳麻痹 身體乏力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.60,0:22:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為我脫胎換骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙在這裏 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.75,0:22:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就表示佐助一定在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:22:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得戰鬥 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:22:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是來救佐助的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.80,0:23:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.60,0:23:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙重鼓動 兜的陷阱
